      <title>亨特·拜登因“偏见”而未能驳回枪支案</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-13/hunter-biden-loses-bid-to-dismiss-firearms-case-over-bias-claim</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一名法官裁定，总统乔·拜登的儿子未能提供证据证明美国政府指控他犯有枪支相关罪行的决定受到了唐纳德·特朗普或其国会盟友的外部影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-13/hunter-biden-loses-bid-to-dismiss-firearms-case-over-bias-claim</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 13 Apr 2024 01:11:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国汽车游说团体称对中国电动汽车征收关税将威胁就业</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/german-auto-lobby-says-tariffs-on-china-evs-would-threaten-jobs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国汽车工业协会表示反对欧盟对从中国进口的电动汽车征收任何关税，称这将冒贸易战的风险并威胁德国的就业。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/german-auto-lobby-says-tariffs-on-china-evs-would-threaten-jobs</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 23:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于巨大的工资差距持续存在，日本年轻工人前往国外</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/japanese-workers-head-overseas-on-working-holiday-visas-lured-by-higher-wages</link>
      <description><![CDATA[吉原智树 (Tomoki Yoshihara) 早上 5 点在澳大利亚乡村的一家肉类加工厂开始值班，每周工作近 50 个小时屠宰羊肉，收入是他在日本军队时的三倍。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/japanese-workers-head-overseas-on-working-holiday-visas-lured-by-higher-wages</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 23:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>被起诉的反对党领袖是韩国的政治赢家</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/indicted-opposition-leader-is-south-korea-s-political-winner</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国主要反对党在议会选举中的胜利，使其领导人成为 2027 年总统的头号竞争者，只要他能够管理善变的公众，并在一场可能会让他入狱的法律斗争中保持领先地位。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/indicted-opposition-leader-is-south-korea-s-political-winner</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 22:00:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普表示支持约翰逊，淡化共和党分歧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/trump-offers-support-for-johnson-as-he-downplays-gop-divisions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[前总统唐纳德·特朗普向陷入困境的众议院议长迈克·约翰逊表示支持，约翰逊在极端保守派议员的压力下努力保住自己的职位，试图平息共和党核心小组的分歧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/trump-offers-support-for-johnson-as-he-downplays-gop-divisions</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 21:46:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>国际货币基金组织总裁格奥尔基耶娃在春季会议前赢得第二任期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/imf-chief-georgieva-wins-second-term-ahead-of-spring-meetings</link>
      <description><![CDATA[克里斯塔利娜·格奥尔基耶娃赢得了国际货币基金组织总裁的第二个五年任期，这使她能够继续领导这家危机贷款机构，以应对全球增长前景黯淡、气候变化和发展中国家不良债务等挑战。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/imf-chief-georgieva-wins-second-term-ahead-of-spring-meetings</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 21:29:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登新规意味着紧凑型荧光灯泡将被淘汰</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/new-biden-rule-means-lights-out-for-compact-fluorescent-bulbs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[紧凑型荧光灯泡——曾经被认为是清洁能源转型的螺旋形标志​​——根据周五敲定的拜登政府规则，该规则将有效地逐步淘汰，该规则对最常用的照明类型提出了新的要求。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/new-biden-rule-means-lights-out-for-compact-fluorescent-bulbs</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 21:08:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>智利将难民遇害事件归咎于委内瑞拉</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/chile-points-finger-at-venezuela-in-case-of-murdered-refugee</link>
      <description><![CDATA[智利政府要求委内瑞拉合作调查一名被谋杀的难民，有迹象表明这起谋杀案是出于政治动机，这考验了两国之间的关系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/chile-points-finger-at-venezuela-in-case-of-murdered-refugee</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 16:14:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴西与中国关系加深，卢拉与亿万富翁 JBS 兄弟重聚</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/lula-reunites-with-billionaire-jbs-brothers-as-brazil-s-china-ties-deepen</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亿万富翁巴蒂斯塔兄弟在被任命为 JBS SA 董事会成员后不到三周，就惊人地卷土重来，将他们推入巴西最高权力圈。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/lula-reunites-with-billionaire-jbs-brothers-as-brazil-s-china-ties-deepen</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 14:54:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马斯克将与莫迪会面，刺激特斯拉投资印度</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-11/tesla-s-musk-to-meet-modi-spurring-india-invesment-speculation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[特斯拉公司首席执行官埃隆·马斯克(Elon Musk)即将访问印度并会见印度总理纳伦德拉·莫迪(Narendra Modi)，这引发了人们对这家美国公司在印度全国大选开始前投资的猜测。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-11/tesla-s-musk-to-meet-modi-spurring-india-invesment-speculation</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Apr 2024 05:55:17 GMT</pubDate>
